{"tid":1926903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共五件事，令你知道香港人若不反抗，則時日無多","createTime":"2020-03-15T12:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T16:16:39.000Z","uid":127735,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a339bdb004395582e430d142a0ac0dba4ac62392","tid":1926903,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"&mdash;　換領新RFID身份證<br />\n&mdash;　增加警察人手<br />\n&mdash;　智能監控燈柱<br />\n&mdash;　23條立法<br />\n&mdash;　電子抄牌<br />\n<br />\n係咪已經無乜人記得換新身份證呢？認真我唸好多人都唔記得左，政府已經暗地裡繼續做緊，換下換下換多一年幾兩年就換曬。前幾日話警察用電子牛肉乾，我心唸知不妙，因為緊接就係電子抄牌，到時再配合埋監控燈柱，又多左警察人手，你係屋企打飛機呀蛇都搵到你呀，示威遊行集會？一個人，一個鐘！都唔洗就咬你番差館，香港以後真係夠曬「太平」囉。<br />\n<br />\n咩話？你想發洩下？無喎，宜家政府買唔到口罩，你係咪想係網上自己買口罩，間接話政府廢同無能，顛覆國家政權，23條極權條例隨時夜晚扔你落鹹水海都得啦，有上述既監控措施，你又唔洗怕呀蛇搵你唔到喎。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，睇路呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97a963300130bc61fede9a3f580778b2f589b42","tid":1926903,"uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:08:01.000Z","msg":"唔推唔知驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7ee0b4569117a7fa4ae94315e2fdc611af1e50","tid":1926903,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ed09e76078ab66333f33ab88bf490b132c1218f","tid":1926903,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab367e05d5737358dc59e4cbfbc668e2f5170caa","tid":1926903,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泛民本土必須有聯合初選<br />\n今次立法會冇過半，前線手足就變Condom"},{"pid":"7ee330674bb7c3